cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.CL 

This paper deals with neural network pruning techniques and their impact on test set accuracy. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) as the paper deals with image classification. The paper also discusses the impact of pruning on different classes and images, which suggests it could also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing). Finally, the paper mentions mislabelled images and fine-grained classification, which could also place it in the cs.CL (Computation and Language) category.
